20001215.description: The Continent that the Character is on has terrains such as mountains, swamps, etc. It is ruled by Human tribes and other intelligent tribes such as the Dragon Tribe.

20002215.description: Polar Island, the island has an erupting volcano. Ancient Beasts, power and mysterious are left on this island.

20003215.description: A world filled with blood and massacre is composed of many Demon Tribes.

20004215.description: A world without light, filled with death and darkness, it is ruled by King Hades, three of his subordinate Fiends are in charge of  Blood, Dark, and Souls, but now they are lost, seeming as though they've been sealed away.

22101216.description: Welcome to participate in Guild City War

1001216.description: Demon Bartos was defeated by Damon, who has infused the power of the Bloody Crystal. Bartos has escaped into the Sunset Mountains. Now that the power of the Bloody Crystal is running out, Bartos must be killed before he recovers.

1002216.description: Undead has appeared upon the peaceful Sunset Mountains, now that the passage to Devildom has opened, my road ahead will much harder.

1003216.description: Passing through the Crystal Lair we're about to arrive at the Barbarian's village. Who knows what happened to the Barbarians after the Demonic invasion at the Sunset Mountains.

1004216.description: Barbarians chose to fight for the Devildom, becoming their underlings. If they chose to betray humans, they no longer serve a purpose to live, let me annihilate them!

2001216.description: The Barbarian Chief has died, but the demonized Barbarians seem much stronger, I need to annihilate them and the intruding demons.

2002216.description: Dragon's Aura, legends say that hundreds of years ago a Green dragon lived in the Sunset Mountains, could it be buried here?

2003216.description: This cave is filled with Demonic Aura, it seems the Barbarians controlled by demons are hidden here, the smell is unbearable.

2004216.description: Finally cleared out that filthy cave, the scenery at the mountain is amazing, but it would be even better without these demons.

2005216.description: The demons built a camp here, looks like the Devildom base at Sunset Mountains.

2006216.description: What a strong demonic aura, looks like someone powerful is here, could it be… Bartos?!

3001216.description: I can't believe Underground City actually exists, how miraculous.

3002216.description: The Fiends within the Bloody Crystal are growing stronger, maybe my soul will also end up being offered to them.

3003216.description: Demons appeared in the Underground City, but they're no match for my blade.

3004216.description: I'm slowly becoming a war machine, slaughtering has become an instinct, am….I still myself? But…. What choice do I have?

3005216.description: In this Gloomy Path, I have no idea how long I've been walking…or how much longer….

3006216.description: Power of Bloodline, what an exciting yet fearful power…..

3007216.description: Frost Demon, the demon in the Forbidden book at the Church has appeared before me, yet my heart has not been moved, it seems….weak….

4001216.description: Maybe only the unknown would cause fear. Legends have become history, but my mission is not yet over.

4002216.description: I've stepped upon Frost Island, it is very cold indeed. It's strange why Bartos would escape to a place as cold as this.

4003216.description: Just as the legends say, the monsters here are all very strong and tempered, is it because they haven't seen fresh meat in a while?

4004216.description: Under the Frozen Island is spurting magma. Miraculous yet unnatural, creatures of evil have filled the cavern under the frozen ice.

4005216.description: It's getting colder, chilling air is continuously blown. Evil aura are evident from these monsters.

4006216.description: These beasts won't attack the demons, could it be that demons can also tame beasts? Or is it some sort of Demonic Magic? It would be nice if teacher was here, sigh.

4007216.description: Hard to believe creatures like such actually exists, there's actually a crab in the magma?!

5001216.description: It's said that the Elven Forest is domain of Succubus, but I wonder if they are as pretty as legends say.

5002216.description: Orcs survival instincts are far stronger than the humans, even such horrifying forests have their tracks.

5003216.description: I'm getting lost in this confusing forest, may the light guide me.

5004216.description: I suddenly remember the days at Sunset Mountains… damned demons, you shall pay!

5005216.description: Tribes without faith are sympathetic, these Orcs finally joined the demons.

5006216.description: I can feel a powerful aura, but I kept feeling that someone is watching my every move!

5007216.description: My feelings were correct, Abyss Demon Beliel, this cunning demon! It won't succeed!

6001216.description: My heart is pounding hard and firm, but…I still feel exhaustion….

6002216.description: Demons, devils, undead….these creatures from the abyss…are hard to tell apart at times.

6003216.description: Hard to imagine how the humans survived the Age of Goblins, it seemed that humans were only slaves.

6004216.description: Endless massacre, my path is filled with blood of Orcs and demons, and corpses of the Undead, I can't see the end of the path.

6005216.description: Sometimes I feel that these fiends of the Underworld are not so evil, they also have kindness in them, has my faith already been swayed?

6006216.description: I found some Ancient Characters in this relic, too bad I'm not an archaeologist, can't understand what they mean.

6007216.description: King of Flames showed me real passion, I'm afraid not many people from this world can experience this passion.

7001216.description: Returning to Frost Island, the demons here are growing stronger, I'm afraid stronger demons have arrived to the human world.

7002216.description: Secretly, I'm beginning to like the smell of blood and…. Massacre…

7003216.description: Such a strong force….I…can't breathe….what is this existence…..angels or revival of Demon God.

7004216.description: I don't know what I'll become…maybe becoming a heresy, burning at the stake…. May light be with me.

7005216.description: Who is it? Revival of Demon God? Or King of Devildom? Of Ancient Demon? Will the humans be able to escape this disaster?!

7006216.description: I can feel the power of darkness in my veins, this powerful, fierce, defying power! I… hope that light can guide my path! Even…even if I can only reside the in darkest of shadows.

7007216.description: Bloodthirsty Brook, what a woeful soul, rest in peace…

8001216.description: King of Devildom Azrael, I won't let you succeed even if I die!

8002216.description: I've entered the legendary Ghastly Jungle, dense leaves has blocked the sky. Surround by grey fog, and a smell of must and rancidity, what's worse is that it is dead silent!

8003216.description: Today I finally see sunlight, but I don't feel any warmness, but…maybe my heart is already cold…

8004216.description: Still nothing from the Heavens, what happened?! Could it be that besides the Devildom, there are other forces of darkness stopping the heavens?!

8005216.description: With the power of Bloody Crystal and endless massacre my strength has grown. But facing the King of Devildom, maybe I'm just a stronger ant to him.

8006216.description: The growth of vines are strange here, it seems like they are one. I kept on feeling that I'm being watched, it's sending chills down my spine, but I still don't know who…or what is behind me….

8007216.description: So it was her, the Mother of Wisp has lived here for tens and thousands of years, maybe the whole jungle is under her watch…. Her appearance is frightening, even female undead look better…

9001216.description: This is where the Demon God lay dormant? It is filled with Goblin atmosphere, who knows how long this place existed.

9002216.description: These demon minions can't stop my path, die! Demons, die!

9003216.description: I can't imagine who can't stop the Demon God once it has awaken?! Maybe only the Guardians of the heavens can.

9004216.description: Blood all over my body are boiling, seemingly…there's a sense of familiarity….Demon God…Blood…what is going on?!

9005216.description: Endless massacres did not exhaust me, it rather got me excited, now I won't be afraid even if I were against the gods!

9006216.description: About to reach the end of the Tomb of Demon God, I can feel a powerful aura, King of Devildom Azrael, I'm here!

9007216.description: Demon God! I won't give up even if I die! No matter I'm using power of darkness, no one can't stop me from standing under the light!

10001216.description: I was transported here by unknown forces when King of Devildom Azrael was defeated. God of Doom called it Sky City. It was built by Angels, really?

10002216.description: Is this heaven or hell? Can't believe I meet Warrior Brooke from Barbarian tribe? Is it a place of reincarnation?

10003216.description: I can't get to the end in this huge city. How can I return to human world?

10004216.description: Is the Barbarian tribe blessed by God? Met the late Barbarian Chief today, hope he's blessed to go to the heavens although he was deluded by demons.

10005216.description: How can the Sky City be created by flawless Angels as the guards here are so ugly...Doom Fiend lied?

10006216.description: Met some sort of God today, another ugly weirdo.

10007216.description: If Sky City was in border of Human world and heaven…I would have a chance to go to heaven directly! But the Fiends wouldn't agree…Angels destroyed the Underworld…

10008216.description: King of Devildom Azrael appeared… Who would be next? King of Heavens?

10009216.description: I don't know how far I still have to go…Might be lost in this huge place.

10010216.description: A soul from nowhere? A transporter? Marvelous. The exit is ahead, but where would it transport me? Human world? Heaven? Or...

10110191.description: Urgh…damn…the power of the Bloody Crystal has exhausted, so that damned demon escaped, what a shame.

10110291.description: Ah Hahaha! Haven't breathed air filled with scent of blood… the human world is wonderful!

10110491.description: I am Blood Fiend, Lord of the Underworld!

10110591.description: Evil souls, get back into the seals!

10110691.description: Oh no, damn seal! Don't do this, dear %self, the scent on your body is very familiar, don't be so cold. I am one of the 5 Lords of the Underworld, I can grant you power! Power of blood!

10110791.description: You've lost your body, with a soul so weak that it's about to dissipate, how can you grant me power?!

10110891.description: Oh! That's only temporarily! Temporarily! Once you've absorbed enough power of souls, letting Dark Fiend, Deceit Fiend, Fear Fiend, and Doom Fiend to awake, they'll grant to even more strength, by then, you can annihilate the Ruler of the Devildom himself!

10110991.description: Remember the words you said today, or else I'll annihilate you myself!

10111091.description: Hahaha, of course, how can I lie to a human, I'm not like Deceit Fiend.

10120291.description: Stranger, leave at once, these are domains of Barbaric Orcs, humans are not welcomed!

10130191.description: The Barbarians are getting stronger, maybe I should rest at the Twilight Stronghold before continuing.

10210191.description: So many Undead creatures, this smell is disgusting.

10210291.description: I think it's actually quite nice, hahaha.

10210391.description: Your smell makes me vomit, you probably haven't showered for thousands of years.

10210591.description: What I meant is that your soul is dirty.

10310291.description: These things are nasty, use your giant feet to squash them.

10310391.description: Do it yourself, just imagining the green fluid oozing out makes me nauseous.

10420291.description: You are a human filled with blood scent, killing so many from the tribe, I'll crush you!

10420391.description: The whole Barbarian tribe is filled with demonic scent…humph, all those who work with demons should be annihilated!

10420491.description: Childish human, Air Splitter Barc makes us stronger!

10420591.description: Air Splitter Barc? He is the leader of Demonic Talon tribe, a vicious fool.

10420691.description: So what, we should get rid of this big guy first.

10430291.description: Tell me where is the Demon Bartos!

10430391.description: Hahaha, you're seeking your own death! Follow the path behind to find Master Barc! Master Air Splitter will revenge us!

10430491.description: Air Splitter Barc? Humph, maybe it'll know the whereabouts of Bartos.

20110192.description: I have a question, if you are so powerful how did you get sealed?

20110292.description: Those from the Heavens outnumbered us, one on one I won't lose to anyone?!

20110392.description: In the documents recorded by the Church says you are the weakest in the Underworld.

20110492.description: Nonsense! All lies from the Heavens!

20110592.description: Oh, I see, you don't have to get so worked up, look those annoying skeletons appeared again.

20210192.description: The air here is so refreshing!

20210292.description: It's filled with the scent of blood, you have a weird appetite.

20210392.description: Hahaha, of course, I am the Blood Fiend!

20310192.description: This place is filled with a weird aura, this aura is making my body more active.

20310392.description: What are you saying? I grew up in the Church, how could I be affiliated with Aura of Darkness!

20310492.description: From the moment Bloody Crystal was fused into your body, the powers in your deepest Bloodlines have been awakened.

20310592.description: Power of the Bloodline? What is that?

20310692.description: The wedge has already been opened, you'll know soon enough. Ok, let's move ahead.

20410192.description: May God grant me strength to annihilate all demons.

20410392.description: Demonic Soul, watch your mouth or forever sink into darkness!

20410492.description: Naive child, you think you're still God's child, a faithful disciple? You had forsaken your faith the moment you unlocked the Bloody Crystal, the power of Darkness within your blood is sufficient for you to be burned at stake ten thousand times!

20410592.description: Shut up! You filthy soul! Go back!

20510192.description: Blood, tell me, what kind of power lie within my Bloodlines?

20510292.description: Actually, I am not positive, but you can awake the power of Bloody Crystal, there must be some sort of miraculous power within your Bloodlines.

20510492.description: Absorb more powers from souls and awake the dormant Doom Fiend, maybe you'll have answers.

20610192.description: Why did the Barbarians fight for the Devildom?

20610292.description: Fight or die, you think they had a choice?

20610392.description: So, was it wrong for me to kill them?

20610492.description: No, no matter what their reasons were, they chose to betray the humans, that makes them the enemy.

20610592.description: Then let them disappear along with the demons from this world.

20620292.description: Oh? You were the one who wounded Bartos? Why do I feel I can kill you with one finger?

20630192.description: Where is Bartos? Why has Devildom invaded! Don't lie to me or I'll have the Bloody Crystal devour your soul!

20630292.description: Nonono!!! I was only sent here to gather information, please let me go! I really don't know anything.

20630392.description: Oh, what a delicious soul, can I eat it?

20630492.description: Oh, no, Bartos is heading towards the Iceland on the outer shores to heal his wounds! No! Please stop! That's all I know! Oh~~ no~~

20630592.description: Frost Island? I'll kill you even if I have to chase you to the Devildom. But before that, let me kill the last demon on Sunset Foothill.

20630692.description: Ha, then his soul belongs to me! Very delicious, if there's another powerful soul like this, save it for me.

20630792.description: The teleporter to Frost Island has been destroyed, looks like we have to go through Underground City.

30110293.description: That's right, pass through here to get to Frost Island.

30210193.description: This place is filled with Undead aura, these undead creatures no longer have souls.

30210293.description: These children are nice, Underground City is connected to the Underworld, the aura is very welcoming to me

30210393.description: Underworld? Wasn't it already defeated by the Heavens?

30210493.description: The power of the Underworld is unimaginable! The heavens were only able to capture a part of it.

30210593.description: But even the 5 Lords of the Underworld…

30210693.description: There are many things you cannot understand, Human complete your mission.

30310193.description: This is beyond imaginations, Centaurs in the Underground City.

30310293.description: Centaurs are a branch of Orcs, so it's possible that they've also gone to the demons.

30410193.description: Fourth day in the Underground City, but according to the map we're only half the way, the Underground City is very vast.

30410293.description: That's right, this Underground City has been here for millions of years.

30410493.description: Of course, at that time humans did not dominate the human world, but the Goblins. This place was created by Goblins and Dwarfs.

30410593.description: Goblin Culture is the most miraculous thing isn't it? It is shocking indeed.

30510193.description: I can feel Deceit Fiend slowly awakening.

30510293.description: Oh! Does that mean I can borrow her powers now?

30510393.description: Not yet, it depends on whether you can supply her with enough souls. But her wisdom will be a lot of help to you.

30510493.description: Really? Then I can't wait to meet her.

30510593.description: I hope that remains the same after you meet her.

30610193.description: It's getting colder, we're nearly there.

30610293.description: No, we're already here, we're underneath Frost Island.

30610393.description: Let's hurry, I'm sick of this place.

30710193.description: Filthy demons, but why are there only minions, they dirtied my weapon with their filthy blood.

30710293.description: Ao..Ao..Ao..Ao… (Wailing sounds are heard from nearby)

30710393.description: Hm? The sound is coming from ahead…

30720293.description: Oh my lord, what are these monsters? Frost beasts?

30720393.description: That is the Lord of Icy Flame Inferno, Frost Demon! Beware of its ice claws, it won't feel good when you get pierce by it.

30720493.description: Icy Flame Inferno? Looks like the Devildom is determined to conquer Human world.

30720593.description: Think later, the big guy is coming!

30730193.description: Let's hurry, we already wasted a week's time, who knows if Bartos is still on Frost Island.

30730293.description: I have a bad feeling about this.

30730493.description: Oh Hahaha! The Mighty Undead Empress is finally awoke, Spirits of the Heavens are you prepared?

40110294.description: Little fellow, you know the Mighty Undead Empress? Hm? Blood, what are you doing?!

40110394.description: The prettiest Empress of the Underworld, meeting you again after thousands of years got me excited…

40110694.description: Humph, then Frost Demon's souls are mine. Dear little fellow, work hard, I'll talk to you once I've absorbed Frost Demon's souls.

40210194.description: Blood, what tribe is Deceit Fiend from? Seems like a Succubus?

40210294.description: Hush… don't say that in front of her, or else…

40210394.description: Then tell me now, I can feel she's concentrated on absorbing energy, she won't be able to hear you.

40210494.description: In fact… Deceit used to be Empress of the Underworld, but then she fell in love with Chaos knight, so she killed the prettiest Succubus and took her body.

40210694.description: Nothing afterwards, all that Chaos knight thinks about are slaughter and destruction, they have no emotions.

40310194.description: It's hard to imagine Frost Island being so cold but underneath are magma.

40310294.description: Little fellow, there are lots you haven't seen. But, this magma seems off, it doesn't seem natural.

40310494.description: Not sure yet, let's look around.

40410194.description: Look at these demonized beasts, they are more bloodthirsty then I am.

40410294.description: They seem stronger than you are.

40410394.description: Don't compare me with these low lives! How can the Great Blood Fiend be compared to these Demonic Beasts.

40410494.description: You were the one comparing first, idiot.

40510194.description: You place last in the 5 Fiends, Deceit Fiend places third, then who is the fourth?

40510294.description: It's Dark, eternal Darkness. Actually, he is already awake.

40510394.description: Oh? Why haven't I heard him speak yet?

40510494.description: Knowing him for hundreds and thousands years, no one has ever seen his appearance, nor heard him speak.

40510594.description: What a weird fellow, you are no match for him right?

40510694.description: If he isn't so fast, making me dizzy, I can beat him with a single punch!

40510794.description: Okay I understood, last place fellow.

40610194.description: Aren't you getting hotter? I feel restless.

40610294.description: You are next to magma, of course it's hot.

40610394.description: No, it's restlessness from the souls.

40610494.description: Little fellow, you are speaking with more abstrusely, you should have been Pope.

40710194.description: Damn it, I feel it, there's a passage to the Devildom! Little fellow you have to destroy it before it opens completely!

40720294.description: This must be entrance to the volcano, I can feel Demonic aura….

40720394.description: Click…Click… (Fiery Blade Overlord is swinging his clamps) who is the fool that dared to intrude Fiery Blade Overlord's domain? Get out.

40730194.description: This big crab is also a Lord of the Icy Flame Inferno?

40730294.description: That's right, Fiery Blade Overlord is the same as Frost Demon, a lord of the Icy Flame Inferno.

40730394.description: Deceit, this passage is protected by Magic Barrier, it'll be hard to destroy with our current strength.

40730494.description: This is…. Hell Moon Magic Barrier, no wonder the only one guarding this place is Fiery Blade Overlord.

40730594.description: Then what do we do now?

40730694.description: Go to the Elven Forest to find the Crystal of Life, that's the most effective way to destroy this Magic Barrier. Let's teleport there now.

50110195.description: My Magic has been exhausted, the rest is up to you little fellow. Don't expect reinforcements from the Heavens either, I felt that the passage from the Heavens to the Human World has just been destroyed.

50110395.description: But be careful, I'm afraid that the demons are already here, since they understand this Magic Barrier better than I do.

50110495.description: Rest assure, I'll defeat them all.

50110595.description: Hopefully….. Knowing you so long, I've never been optimistic about you….

50210195.description: This damp weather makes me weak, scales are all becoming soft.

50210295.description: Scales? You are just a soul, you don't have scales.

50210395.description: When you've worn the same clothes for thousands of years, you'll understand.

50310195.description: How many days have we been in the forest?

50310295.description: Four? Or five days? Can't remember.

50310395.description: It seems we're lost, I remember being here before.

50310595.description: Maybe we can try following the path where monsters are appearing.

50410195.description: Ha, you know what, I'm hungry again!

50410395.description: Of course I do! But only the Great Blood Fiend eats, the rest don't enjoy life.

50410495.description: Then what do you usually eat?

50410595.description: Sausage made by Ghouls, meat sauce made by insects, bone nectar collected by frenzy moths, and….

50510195.description: I hate Orcs more and more, can't never seem to get rid of them.

50510295.description: Don’t mind them, hurry and find the Crystal of Life.

50610295.description: Hm, I feel a strong life force ahead.

50610395.description: Hurry, we've wasted too much time.

50710195.description: Human, the Crystal of Life is mine, Ah Hahahaha!

50710295.description: Demon! Damn it, I thought something felt wrong, can't believe he is ahead of us!

50710395.description: Oh it's Abyss Demon Beliel! But, you seem a bit weak?!

50710495.description: Quit rambling, hurry and finish him and get the Crystal of Life.

50730195.description: Crystal of Life, we've finally got it.

50730295.description: Great work little fellow. Next we have to go through the Underground City again to get back to Frost Island.

60110196.description: I would've never thought I could see the Underground City again.

60110296.description: When we were sealed, we've never thought we would be out again.

60110396.description: Angels, one day I will pluck all angels' feathers!

60210196.description: Underground City is now filled with demons, looks like many Demons arrived during this time.

60210296.description: No matter, the passage is not completed opened, powerful demons can't enter yet, so hurry.

60310196.description: Why does I feel the Underground City is much hotter than last time?

60310296.description: I can't feel hot or cold, ah hahaha!

60310396.description: Quiet, muscle fool. The Underground City does seem strange, be careful, little fellow.

60310496.description: Give me more souls and Great Blood wouldn't mind fight for you!

60410196.description: I think…. I know why Underground City has gotten so much hotter.

60410396.description: Frost Demon and Fiery Blade Overlord of Icy Flame Inferno were both killed by you, then as the Leader of the Icy Flame Inferno, King of Flames Bartos obviously wouldn't sit still.

60410496.description: King of Flames Bartos? Did he get through the passage?!

60410596.description: I don't know, maybe I'm wrong.

60410696.description: No matter what, I can't retreat, must seal the passage before the Demonic Army arrives, or else it will be disastrous.

60510396.description: In just over a month, you have advanced from a little soldier to one of the stronger humans ever.

60510496.description: You've seen it too, I've been faced with death many times during this period.

60510596.description: Blood, this little fellow is not a normal human, something in his blood hold horrific power.

60510696.description: What is that power? Please tell me, Deceit.

60510796.description: I'm not positive, I only know that the one with this power is far stronger than I am.

60510896.description: Don't think about it, you'll know once our Boss awakes. Boss has been alive even before the birth of the underworld.

60610196.description: I'm afraid I was right, I can already smell the smoke from the King of Flames.

60610296.description: If he wants death then I'll send him to hell just like I did with his minions.

60610396.description: Don't underestimate him, King of Flames Bartos is much stronger than your imagination, it's not comparable to those two you killed earlier.

60610496.description: I know, but I have no other choice.

60720296.description: Human fellow, you were the one that killed these two idiots?

60720496.description: Revenge? Nono, they were only my pets, but by killing my pets you offended my dignity! For that you must pay!

60720596.description: Bartos, long time no see, it seems you still haven't gotten any smarter after all these years.

60720696.description: Deceit Fiend?! Weren't you sealed! Oh, you are just a soul, ah Hahahaha, what nice nutrients.

60720796.description: Idiot, being a henchman for the Devildom for thousands of years you still an idiot. Little fellow, you're up.

60730196.description: Damn, this is just a Mirror!

60730296.description: You can't kill me! I vow in the name of Leader of the Icy Flame Inferno, I will burn your souls!

60730396.description: Get out of here, you idiot, you dare act tough in front of the Great Blood Fiend!

60730496.description: Ok, now let us destroy this Magic Barrier and seal the passage!

70110197.description: No, so many demons, can't it be that the Demonic army is already through the passage!

70110297.description: The passage is fluctuation strongly, I can't confirm the status of the passage, let's hurry.

70210197.description: Ha, fellow, do you smell something familiar?

70210297.description: My nose is not as good as your, you dog.

70210397.description: Great Blood Fiend is not kidding with you, don't you smell this strong scent of blood!

70210497.description: Now that you mentioned it, I do smell it, why is that?

70210597.description: How am I suppose to know! Let's just go!

70310197.description: I do feel a bit nervous, is something about to happen?

70310297.description: I've been feeling a strong aura recently.

70310397.description: Could it be someone powerful from the Devildom?

70310497.description: Or maybe someone from the Heavens.

70310597.description: Really? Looks like the demons will finally be defeated.

70310697.description: Humph, that's not necessary something good, don’t forget that you're now filled with Fiendish power! Little fellow!

70410197.description: This strong scent of blood is so relaxing.

70410297.description: It seems… this scent is coming from the cave ahead.

70410397.description: With such a strong scent, it seems there may be a big fellow inside the cave, ah hahaha.

70510197.description: Little fellow, I have a bad news for you.

70510397.description: I'm araid that powerful fellow isn't from the Heavens, hahaha!

70510597.description: It seems so, but I have another good news!

70510797.description: That fellow has already left Frost Island, so you won't have to face him now. With your power right now, you'll be defeated in seconds.

70510897.description: Humph, if so then let's seal the Demonic Passage now.

70610197.description: If one day the demons are forced back to the Devildom, then where would I go?

70610297.description: Oh? Why has the little fellow become so sentimental? Think about it when that day does come! Hahaha.

70720297.description: I was thinking why the aura is so familiar, it's an Orc!

70720397.description: Growl! I am the number one Warrior of Orcs, Bloodthirsty Brook! Who are you?!

70720497.description: Dogs of the demons, Orc? You are know a watchdog of demons?

70720597.description: Growl! ! The Mighty Brook had just been demonized, prepare to die puny human!

70730297.description: Oh? Did he get hit in his head?

70730397.description: Human…..we've been tricked….the demons infused demonic power into us, controlling our thought….we shouldn't have taken refuge with the demons…

70730497.description: Humph, traitors never end up well,  you should have known this.

70730597.description: Listen to me… the King of Devildom is already in the human world, he is going to the Tomb of Demon God to revive the Demon God's soul, hurry… stop him!

70730697.description: What!!! Where is the Tomb of Demon God? Tell me!

80110298.description: This should be it, there's a mysterious power surrounding this place, I can't teleport here.

80110398.description: Ok, hopefully King of Devildom hasn't entered the Tomb of Demon God yet.

80210198.description: Little fellow, I have something to tell you.

80210398.description: With your current strength, I'm afraid you are no match to the King of Devildom, even if you found him you won't be able to stop him.

80210498.description: I have to do whatever I can, if I don't go and the Demon God awakes the human world will be conquered, I have no choice but to go.

80310198.description: This damned jungle, I'm losing patience!

80310298.description: Legends say that no one has ever gotten out of Ghastly Jungle, it's like a labyrinth.

80310398.description: So what, our enemy is the legendary demon! And you guys are the legendary fiends of the Underworld!

80310498.description: Oh….guess you're right…we are even more of a legend, hahaha!

80410198.description: Tell me more about the King of Devildom, just how strong is he?

80410298.description: King of Demons Azrael is the number one servant of the Demon God, his power… maybe only Doom Fiend can rival.

80410398.description: Doom Fiend, head of the 5 Fiends…okay I understand…

80510198.description: If there's a chance, I'll show you around the Underworld.

80510298.description: What's to see at the Underworld?

80510398.description: Ha, there are lots! Let me tell you…

80510498.description: Stop, we have important things to do.

80510598.description: Who knows if I would still be alive then….

80510698.description: Rest assure, the Great Blood Fiend is here, ah Hahahaha!

80610198.description: Have you noticed that the vines around us are all growing toward the same direction.

80610298.description: It seems we're nearly at the jungle's center.

80720298.description: Welcome to the Ghastly Jungle, young human.

80720498.description: I am the master of this jungle, Mother of Wisp, are you here for the demon?

80720698.description: Oh! That I cannot tell you, the King of Devildom has done me a big favor, so now I cannot let you leave.

80720798.description: Do you even know what he is trying to do! He is going to awake the Demon God!

80720898.description: Oh…What does that have to do with me? The Human World is not easy to destroy, young fellow.

80720998.description: Damn it, no time to chat with you, if you stand in my way then don't blame me.

80730198.description: The Tomb of Demon God is behind there, hurry.

80730298.description: Ok, King of Demons Azrael, I won't let you succeed!

90110199.description: So this is the Tomb of Demon God, I wonder what the Demon God looks like.

90110299.description: I don't think you would want to see him.

90210199.description: Such a strong  force, I can barely breathe.

90210299.description: It's because you're too weak, muscle fool.

90310199.description: I wonder when the Heavens will break the seal and force the demons back where they belong.

90310299.description: Eh… something is wrong, it's been so long, with their powers they should have broken through already….

90310399.description: Could it be that the Heavens are already here?

90310499.description: No….no, I would be able to feel him if he is here. There must be some sort of secret here.

90410199.description: Did you guys feel that sudden strong wave!

90410299.description: Of course, such a strong wave, could it be that the Demon God is already awake?!

90410399.description: No….no way….hurry! We have to stop him!

90510199.description: Actually, I don't even know what I can do when I see the King of Devildom.

90510299.description: Oh, little fellow, you are already strong! With your current strength maybe you'll be able to rival him.

90510399.description: Sigh, we're already here and there's no way back. Let's go, even if it is hell awaiting for us.

90510499.description: Hell is not that scary, ah hahaha.

90610199.description: I can feel it, the strong aura is just ahead, we're nearly there.

90610299.description: Hopefully he hasn't awaken the Demon God yet, may God bless the human world.

90720299.description: The Mighty Demon God is already awake, ah Hahahaha!

90720499.description: No, we still have a chance! The Demon God's body is not here, which means….

90720599.description: The insects of the Underworld are here too? You're right, the Mighty Demon God will be revived in the Devildom, but you won't live until then.

90720699.description: Humph, little fellow, don't be afraid, awaking the Demon God made him weaker, use this chance to kill him, then we'll go to the Devildom, Demon God's revival takes a long time!

90720799.description: Foolish, you actually think you can defeat the King of Devildom!

90730199.description: Demon God… is immortal…. Devildom…is eternal!!!

100110200.description: It seems we've left the human world? Where did the King of Devildom transport us to?

100110300.description: Yes, this is the Sky City.

100110500.description: This is the border of heaven and human world, which created by angels to exile fallen souls from heaven.

100110600.description: How do we return to human world?

100110700.description: Not sure, let's see what's ahead.

100210400.description: It's Bloodthirsty Brook, I recognize this scent of blood from miles away.

100210600.description: Who knows, anything can happen in the angel's domain.

100310200.description: It's Brook, how did he revive?

100310300.description: It's said Heaven's Council gather souls of the strong and make them puppets. But there must be a flaw, Brook is just a killing machine.

100310400.description: But he is much stronger than before!

100410200.description: Looks like we meet old enemy.

100410400.description: Not sure, but I'm familiar with the smell.

100510500.description: Would guardian know how to return to Human world?

100610200.description: Did Angels really create the Sky City?

100610300.description: Precisely it was created by King of Heavens and the Heaven's Council.

100610500.description: Just like I'm the King of Underworld and Azrael is the King of Devildom.

100610600.description: I defeated the strongest of Devildom?!

100610700.description: Haha, not yet, that was just an image of Azrael in the Human world.

100610800.description: …..One day I will go to the Devildom and annihilate the demon!

100710200.description: Why is Sky City like a maze?

100710300.description: Did we just go in a circle?

100710400.description: Keep moving forward, I feel the end is nearing.

100810200.description: Hm? I feel a special aura of soul here.

100810400.description: Yeah… Aura I've never felt before… interesting.

100910200.description: Can't believe the heavens found Azrael's soul fragment.

100910300.description: How dare King of Devildom intrude human world with a scapegoat, one day Devildom will be destroyed completely.

100910500.description: Why not, even the Underworld disappeared!

100910600.description: Heaven, Human world, Devildom are the fundamentals of the World. The Underworld was just an attachment, it's not the same.

100910800.description: Then a new King of Devildom will be borne? Hahaha, interesting.

101010400.description: My soul came from nowhere and was locked here for thousands of years.

101010500.description: Do you know how to get out of here?

101010600.description: Save your breath, I've been here too long, let's fight first!

101030200.description: Hahaha, thank you, my soul is finally freed from here.

101030400.description: There's a transporter ahead, but not sure where it leads to…Goodbye, friend…
